# 3. Fixing Incorrect Data Types

## Definition

Machine learning algorithms require correct data types.

Example:

Rating = "eight"

Stored as text instead of number.

---

## Solution

Convert:

Object

↓

Numeric

---

# Example

Movie Recommendation Project

Rating:

"eight"

↓

